{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389870/extras/Debate_preview.gif?t=1736188719\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Artificial Selection</strong> is a multi-route mystery visual novel with escape room puzzles set in a distant future where the <strong>death penalty</strong> is commonplace. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game is currently under development, but the entire <strong>first route</strong> of the game can be played <strong>for free</strong> in form of the <strong>Demo</strong>. <strong>Wishlist the game to be notified when it's ready!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389870/extras/story.png?t=1736188719\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Saeva</strong>, a socially anxious teenager, finds himself trapped in a building along with <strong>13 other &quot;Sinners&quot;</strong>. Their <strong>captors</strong> accuse them of being <strong>criminals </strong>and explain that the only way to escape is by proving their worth and potential for improvement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The only problem is... Saeva <strong>can't think of any crime</strong> he's supposed to have committed. How do you repent for something you can't remember doing?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Help him recover his memories and unravel the underlying mystery \u2014 all while trying not to die!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389870/extras/features.png?t=1736188719\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389870/extras/escape.gif?t=1736188719\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Solve escape room puzzles! </strong> <br>Exercise your brain and build a sense of solidarity with the other participants by overcoming various tasks together.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>There are 14 hot singles in your confined area! </strong>   <br>Dive deep into the psychology and philosophy of 14 different (supposed) criminals. Play your cards right, and you might even get to romance them!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Prove your debate skills! </strong>   <br>The majority decides who gets left behind, so it's up to you to convince them who that is. Change the tides of a debate by strategically attacking or defending the right opponents.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A highly complex flowchart! </strong><br>Keep track of affection opportunities you might have missed, get a quick story recap whenever you need one, and easily jump back and forth between all the branching paths you've unlocked.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Bisexual lighting! </strong><br>A heavily stylized blue, pink and purple environment surrounds you every step of the way. Heaps of customization options allow you to adjust the game's look to your liking.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389870/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736188719","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389870/page.bg.jpg?t=1736188719","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389870/38132c23d033c3bb94cc53bc6848632e14025819/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736188719","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1389870/38132c23d033c3bb94cc53bc6848632e14025819/capsule_184x6